RawLine: SDM_2103016202,開封鏢局歷史悠久，有祖傳名刀「天靈」一把，只傳給歷代鏢頭使用，乃天地忠義，萬物靈性之象徵。,开封镖局历史悠久，有祖传名刀「天灵」一把，只传给历代镖头使用，乃天地忠义，万物灵性之象征。

Items.mt: The Kaifeng Darts Board has a long history and has a famous ancestral sword "Tian Ling", which was only handed down to the head of the darts, a symbol of the loyalty and righteousness of heaven and earth and the spirituality of all things.
